ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 161 - (Saskatchewan) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 161 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING throughout the major watersheds of the province on March 31, 2011.
